        "content": "## S4 \u00b7 02 \u00b7 Status Codes Lab\n\nEvery HTTP node here has **Continue On Fail** enabled.\nWithout it, the workflow stops on the first 401 and you can't compare results.\n\n**Codes you'll see:**\n- 200 \u2014 OK (valid call)\n- 401 \u2014 Unauthorized (bad API key)\n- 404 \u2014 Not Found (wrong path)\n- 422 \u2014 Unprocessable (missing field)\n\nStatus codes are **information**, not failure.",
